item.title: CVE-2019-3737|2024-09-16T19:50:59.459Z -- dell%20emc -- avamar
item.description: Dell EMC Avamar ADMe Web Interface 1.0.50 and 1.0.51 are affected by an LFI vulnerability which may allow a malicious user to download arbitrary files from the affected system by sending a specially crafted request to the Web Interface application.
